        <h2 class="artical-title">The Four Cs of a Diamond</h2>
        <p>Every diamond, whether lab-grown or mined, is classified using 4 Cs – cut, carat, colour and clarity. We may have all heard these terms before, but let’s take a minute to understand what they mean and how they affect the quality of our diamonds.</p>
